      "text": "ここが、主人公が仲間に裏切られた場所なんよね\n悲哀や葛藤が蘇ってくる感じ、ぞくぞくするわぁ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is the place where the main character was betrayed by his friend\nIt feels like sadness and conflict are coming back‚ it's thrilling~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
