      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon",
      "startTime": 23.5666687648
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_03-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "え？　瑠依ちゃん？\nなんでここにおるん？　今日はお仕事ちゃうん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? Rui-chan?\nWhat are you doing here? Aren't you supposed to be working today?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.5666687648,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon",
      "startTime": 29.4333354314
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_03-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "この辺で撮影があったの。ちょうどさっき終わったのよ\n優は今日オフよね。こんな所で何してるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was filming around here. I just finished\nYu‚ today was your day off. What are you doing here?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.4333354314,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon",
      "startTime": 38.1666687648
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_03-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "うち、漫画の聖地巡りしとったんよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I‚ was doing a pilgrimage to the manga",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.1666687648,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon",
