      "text": "漫画のモデルになった場所に実際に行って歩いたり\n同じ構図で写真を撮ったり、同じものを食べたり……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Going to the places that were used as models for the manga‚ and walking around‚\nand taking photos from the same angles‚ and eating the same things…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.7333361944,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon",
      "startTime": 52.8666687649
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_03-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "はっ！　待って、今、瑠依ちゃんがいる場所\nヒロインが声を掛けてくれた所と全く一緒やん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hah! Wait‚ the place where Rui-chan is right now\nIt's exactly the same place where the heroine was when she spoke!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.8666687649,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon",
