      "text": "はぁ～！　うちの好きな漫画の聖地で\nうちの好きな瑠依ちゃんと出会えるなんて……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haa~! I got to meet my favorite Rui-chan\nin the sanctuary of my favorite comics…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.5000008267,
